Supports Story: #100

    Empty Leaderboard:
        Verify that when the game is launched for the first time, the leaderboard is empty.

    Score Submission:
        Play the game and achieve a score.
        Verify that the score is correctly submitted to the leaderboard.

    Maximum Score Display:
        Achieve the maximum possible score in the game.
        Verify that the maximum score is displayed at the top of the leaderboard.

    Minimum Score Display:
        Submit a score of zero or the lowest possible score.
        Verify that the minimum score is displayed correctly on the leaderboard.

    Multiple Score Submission:
        Play the game multiple times and achieve different scores.
        Verify that all scores are accurately displayed on the leaderboard in descending order.

